com.threerings.presents.peer.server
Interface NodeRequestsListener.NodeRequestsResult<T>

Enclosing interface:
NodeRequestsListener<T>
public static interface NodeRequestsListener.NodeRequestsResult<T>

Contains the result of a PeerManager.NodeRequest sent to one or more peer nodes. Any node that returned true for PeerManager.NodeRequest.isApplicable(com.threerings.presents.peer.data.NodeObject) will appear in either getNodeResults() or getNodeErrors(). The wasDropped() method will return true iff both mappings are empty.
